<P>THE
Convocation:
OR, A
Battle of Pamphlets.
A
POEM.</P>
<P>Written by
Mr. <HI>RICHARD SAVAGE.</HI></P>
<Q>For thee the Prelate will his Church betray.</Q>
<BIBL><HI>How</HI>'s Panegyrick on K. <HI>W.</HI></BIBL>
<P><HI>LONDON,</HI>
Printed for <HI>E. Young,</HI> at the <HI>Angel</HI> near <HI>Lincolns-Inn</HI>
Back-Gate; and Sold by <HI>J. Morphew,</HI> near Statiouers
Hall. 1717.</P>
<P>Price 6 <HI>d.</HI></P>
